race.description: Swan Reach Hotel Mindarie-Halidon Cup Hcp
race.comment: Strong edition of the feature race. Hard to go past the very much in-form SUPER LAD (2) who has won his last three. No doubt aimed at this but the lead-up form couldn't have been more impressive including the Morphettville win last time. Will take running down. THERMODYNAMIC (5) wasn't far away last time and did win only other try this trip. Will be winding up late. BIT OF A REBEL (6) won this last year as a very inexperienced horse and returns in solid form. Runner-up in the Jamestown Cup as the lead up and can go close again. BACK ME UP BENNY (9) has been in great recent form and is weighted to feature.
